cs.CR, cs.NI, cs.DC, cs.SE, cs.SY 

This paper discusses the security of network functions and server applications in the cloud, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) and network infrastructure (cs.NI). The paper also proposes a solution using Intel's Software Guard Extensions (SGX) architecture, which involves hardware and system design (cs.DC) and software engineering (cs.SE). Finally, the paper evaluates the proposed solution in terms of performance, which relates to systems and control (cs.SY).
